      "message": "[[maybe_unused]] can be applied unconditionally to the parameter. When PCIe is enabled, the attribute is harmless. When PCIe is disabled, it suppresses the unused-parameter warning. The #ifdef/#endif wrapper is unnecessary and adds noise — 3 lines can be reduced to 1.",
